<%
  const breadcrumbs = [
    { name: "Home", href: "/" },
    { name: "Truck Hearse vs Traditional Hearse", href: "/truck-hearse-vs-traditional-hearse" }
  ];
%>

<%- include('partials/head', {
  title,
  metaTitle,
  metaDescription,
  canonicalPath,
  breadcrumbs
}) %>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<%
  const s = settings || {};
  const phoneRaw = String(s.phone || "").trim();
  const phoneTel = phoneRaw.replace(/\s+/g, "");
%>

<div class="wrap">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 style="color: var(--accent);">Truck Hearse vs Traditional Hearse</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Choosing between a truck hearse and a traditional hearse is often about finding the funeral vehicle
      that best reflects the life, personality, and story of the person being remembered.
    </p>

    <div class="cta" style="margin:18px 0 8px;">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Enquire</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/gallery">View gallery</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/faq">FAQ</a>
      <% if (phoneTel) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="tel:<%= phoneTel %>">Call <%= phoneRaw %></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">What is the difference between a truck hearse and a traditional hearse?</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        A traditional hearse is the familiar funeral vehicle most people expect to see at a service. It offers
        a classic and conventional appearance that suits many funerals. A truck hearse, by contrast, provides
        a more individual and visually distinctive alternative while still maintaining dignity, respect, and professionalism.
      </p>
      <p>
        The choice between a truck hearse and a traditional hearse often depends on the person being remembered.
        For someone whose life was closely linked to haulage, transport, engineering, logistics, or heavy vehicles,
        a truck hearse can feel far more personal and meaningful than a conventional funeral car.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">When a truck hearse may be the right choice</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Families often choose a truck hearse when they want the final journey to reflect a loved one’s character,
        career, or lifelong interests. It can be especially fitting for professional drivers, mechanics, transport
        workers, haulage business owners, and people who simply loved trucks and life on the road.
      </p>
      <p>
        In these situations, a truck hearse becomes more than transport. It becomes part of the tribute itself,
        helping the funeral feel more personal and more closely connected to the life being celebrated.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">When a traditional hearse may be preferred</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        A traditional hearse may be preferred where families want a more familiar and understated style.
        For some funerals, convention and simplicity feel most appropriate, and a traditional hearse delivers that
        classic appearance.
      </p>
      <p>
        Choosing a traditional hearse does not mean the funeral is any less personal. It simply reflects a different
        preference in tone and presentation. The right choice is the one that feels most appropriate for the person
        and the family.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">A more personal final journey</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        For many families, the key benefit of a truck hearse is that it helps create a final journey that stands apart
        from the ordinary. It offers real presence, individuality, and a strong visual tribute while still supporting
        a respectful funeral service.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are comparing a truck hearse with a traditional hearse, the most helpful question is often not which is
        better in general, but which is more fitting for the person being remembered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Explore related pages</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><a href="/lorry-hearse-hire-uk">Lorry hearse hire across the UK</a></p>
      <p><a href="/renault-magnum-hearse">Renault Magnum hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/erf-ec12-hearse">ERF EC12 hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/case-studies">Truck hearse case studies</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
